WEBVTT

00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:31.202
Kada sam bila mlađa,

00:00:31.226 --> 00:00:33.439
željela sam izgledati kao Betsey Johnson.

00:00:33.463 --> 00:00:36.806
Vjerovala sam da smo
srodne duše čupavih frizura.

00:00:37.415 --> 00:00:39.373
Završila sam modni dizajn

00:00:39.397 --> 00:00:41.956
i radila u modnoj industriji niz godina,

00:00:41.980 --> 00:00:43.237
obožavala sam to.

00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:45.112
Udala sam se

00:00:45.136 --> 00:00:46.701
i dobila troje djece.

00:00:47.746 --> 00:00:51.439
Ali život zna biti okrutno ironičan.

00:00:53.779 --> 00:00:58.549
Srednje dijete, Oliver, rođen je
s rijetkim oblikom mišićne distrofije,

00:00:58.573 --> 00:00:59.726
skraćeno MD.